    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Home Training Is Neglected by Many</strong>&mdash;Notwithstanding boasted advancement that has been made in educational methods, the training of children at the present day is sadly defective. It is the home training that is neglected. Parents, and especially mothers, do not realize their responsibility. They have neither the patience to instruct nor the wisdom to control the little ones entrusted to their keeping.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"ST 3-11-1886\" data-link=\"820.7012\">The Signs of the Times, March 11, 1886</span>.</span></a></sup>",
