    "content": "Before visitors, before every other consideration, your children should come first.... The labor due your child during its early years will admit of no neglect. There is no time in its life when the rule should be forgotten.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">10<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CT 129.1\" data-link=\"23.603\">Counsels to Teachers, Parents, and Students, 129</span>.</span></a></sup>",
