    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Mothers to Be Models of Goodness and Nobility</strong>&mdash;Mothers, be careful of your precious moments. Remember that your children are passing forward where they may be beyond your educating and training. You may be to them the very model of all that is good and pure and noble. Identify your interest with theirs.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">12<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 9-15-1891\" data-link=\"821.11491\">The Review and Herald, September 15, 1891</span>.</span></a></sup>",
